  "prompt": "Do any of the Indian banks provide personalized gift cards where I can put a personalized image on the card?",
  "response": "Yes, several Indian banks offer personalized gift card options that allow you to customize the card with your own images or messages. Here are some prominent options:\n\n### **1. ICICI Bank \u2013 Clix Gift Cards**\n**ICICI Bank** provides **Clix Gift Cards** which are highly customizable. You can:\n- **Upload Personal Images:** Add your own photos to make the gift card unique.\n- **Personal Messages:** Include a personalized message for the recipient.\n- **Multiple Designs:** Choose from various designs or themes to suit the occasion.\n\n**How to Order:**\n- **Online:** Visit the [ICICI Clix Gift Card](https://www.icicibank.com) section on the ICICI website or their Clix platform.\n- **Branches:** You can also visit any ICICI Bank branch to purchase and customize the gift card in person.\n\n### **2. HDFC Bank \u2013 Regalia Prepaid Gift Card**\n**HDFC Bank** offers the **Regalia Prepaid Gift Card**, which can be personalized to some extent.\n- **Design Selection:** Choose from a variety of designs available for different occasions like birthdays, anniversaries, and festivals.\n- **Custom Messaging:** Add a personal message to accompany the gift card.\n\n**How to Order:**\n- **Online:** Through the [HDFC Bank website](https://www.hdfcbank.com) under the prepaid cards section.\n- **Branches:** Available at HDFC Bank branches for in-person customization.\n\n### **3. State Bank of India (SBI) \u2013 SBI Gift Cards**\n**SBI** provides **SBI Gift Cards** that offer some customization features.\n- **Design Choices:** Select from various pre-designed templates suitable for different occasions.\n- **Personal Messages:** Add a personalized note to the recipient.\n\n**How to Order:**\n- **Online:** Visit the [SBI Gift Card](https://www.onlinesbi.com) portal on the SBI website.\n- **Branches:** Available at selected SBI branches for direct customization.\n\n### **4. Axis Bank \u2013 Prepaid Gift Cards**\n**Axis Bank** offers prepaid gift cards with some customization options.\n- **Design Variations:** Choose from multiple designs tailored for different events.\n- **Personal Messages:** Include a personal message with the gift card.\n\n**How to Order:**\n- **Online:** Through the [Axis Bank website](https://www.axisbank.com) under the prepaid products section.\n- **Branches:** Purchase and customize at Axis Bank branches.\n\n### **Alternative Options: Third-Party Services**\nIf you're looking for more extensive personalization (like uploading your own high-resolution images), you might consider third-party services that specialize in personalized gift cards in India. These platforms often offer:\n- **Advanced Customization:** Full control over the card\u2019s appearance, including photo uploads.\n- **Wide Range of Templates:** Extensive gallery of templates for various occasions.\n- **Flexible Delivery Options:** Both physical and digital gift cards.\n\n**Popular Third-Party Platforms:**\n- **GiftstoIndia24x7**\n- **Fabbay**\n- **Giftcart**\n\n**How to Use:**\n- Visit the chosen third-party website.\n- Select the gift card option and choose the level of personalization you desire.\n- Upload your images and customize the message as needed.\n- Complete the purchase and choose delivery method (email, physical card, etc.).\n\n### **Tips for Personalization:**\n- **High-Quality Images:** Ensure the image you upload is high-resolution to avoid pixelation.\n- **Occasion-Specific Designs:** Choose designs that resonate with the occasion (e.g., birthdays, weddings).\n- **Clear Messaging:** Keep your personal message concise and heartfelt.\n\n### **Conclusion**\nWhile major Indian banks like **ICICI**, **HDFC**, **SBI**, and **Axis Bank** offer personalized gift card options with customizable designs and messages, the extent of personalization (such as uploading your own images) may vary. For more extensive customization, third-party services might be the best alternative. It\u2019s recommended to visit the respective bank\u2019s website or contact their customer service for the most up-to-date and detailed information regarding their gift card offerings.",
  "response_tokens": [
